SIMPLE: availableness
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Availableness
<hw>A*vail"a*ble*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Competent
power; validity; efficacy; <as>as, the <ex>availableness</ex> of a
title</as>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Quality of being available; capability of being used
for the purpose intended.</def> <rj><au>Sir M. Hale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Avaiably</ent>⟦br⟧
